product.name: SMS Updates
product.description:
Currently in Beta
This service allows you to send text messages to our system and retrieve quick stats about your streams.

Current Keywords
"Playing" - Texts you back the current track playing.
"Listeners" - How many listeners are currently tuned in to all mounts.
"Status" - Stream Status, is it up, is everything functioning normal.
"Skipsong" - Skips the currently playing song.

Thats only the start as this is in BETA, we will be building on this as time passes and are aiming towards being able to control a lot of the functions on your stream via text message keywords.
